mali-valhall-g610 (1.0.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian packaging of the Rockchip Mali-Valhall (CSF) DKMS module.
  * Builds valhall_kbase.ko (Mali-G610, platform rk, ARM DDK g29p1) on mainline
    ARM64 kernels via DKMS, installed to /usr/src/mali-valhall-g610-g29p1.
  * Ships the rockchip-drm render-node, system-uncached dma-heap, and optional
    GPU page-migration kernel patches under kernel-patches/ (see README.md).

 -- Ivan Podogov <ginkage.uk@gmail.com>  Tue, 30 Jun 2026 16:08:22 +0100
